=== Pre-existing language definitions
#info[Check out the #link("https://typst.app/universe/package/codly-languages")[`codly-languages`] package on Typst universe. It contains pre-definition for many language and is extremely easy to use. You can consider it officially endorsed by the codly author as of the 19th of November 2024.]

#example(````typ
#import "@preview/codly-languages:0.1.1": *
#codly(languages: codly-languages)
```rust
fn main() {
  println!("Hello, world!");
}
```
```zig
const std = @import("std");

pub fn main() void {
  std.debug.print("Hello, world!", .{});
}
```
