annotations.example:
#codly(
  annotations:(
    (
      start: 1, end: 4,
      content: block(
        width: 2em,
        rotate(-90deg, reflow: true, 
          align(center)[Function body])
      )
    ),
  ),
)
```py
def fib(n):
  if n <= 1:
    return n
  else:
    return fib(n - 1) + fib(n - 2)
fib(25)
```

highlights.example:
#codly(highlights: (
  (line: 3, start: 2, end: none, fill: red),
  (line: 4, start: 13, end: 19, fill: green, tag: "(a)"),
  (line: 4, start: 26, fill: blue, tag: "(b)"),
))
```py
def fib(n):
 if n <= 1:
  return n
 else:
  return fib(n - 1) + fib(n - 2)
print(fib(25))
```
